Øyvind.definition: A very addictive central [stimulating] substance. People doing Øyvind is often [recognized] walking around with extreme euphoria. Interviews with people doing øyvind says its a very extreme experience, but the downside is that [everything] and everyone else seems dull in comparison.
Øyvind.example:
[I just] had [a piece] of Øyvind... [AWSOME]!
I need some more Øyvind...
